<help general practice>

This is how you gain the ability to do skills and spells.  A
guildmaster of your class must be present to teach you.  If
given no arguments, practice will show you what you already know. 

Syntax:  practice [spell/skill] <<<<i_th> [teacher]>

Example:  practice illumminate		Teaches you illuminate
	  practice			Same as 'abilities'.
<color=red>
See Also:  abilities, score
</color></help>
